# bt_api_kraken

Kraken exchange package for `bt_api`.

## Installation

```bash
pip install bt_api_kraken
```

## Usage

When installed alongside `bt_api_py`, the package is discovered automatically by the unified plugin loader.

## Supported Exchanges

- KRAKEN___SPOT
- KRAKEN___FUTURES
